NB: after the Apertura but before the Clausura, the general assembly of the
    clubs did not authorize Villa Española to continue playing without
    having an own field.  (A 2/3rd majority would have been required.)  As a
    consequence, Villa Española will not be allowed to play in the
    Clausura (all matches are awarded walkovers against them) and they are
    relegated to the third level (Liga Metropolitana Amateur) for 2001.

